'''天主教卡利亚里总教区'''是[[罗马天主教|罗马天主教]]在意大利撒丁岛设立的一个总教区，主教座堂设在[[卡利亚里|卡利亚里]]。它是卡利亚里教省的中心<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/diocese/dcagl.html |title=''Catholic Hierarchy'' page |accessdate=2008-10-28 |archive-date=2019-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330232130/http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/diocese/dcagl.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，附属教区由[[天主教伊格萊西亞斯教區|伊格莱西亚斯教区]]、[[天主教拉努塞伊教區|拉努塞伊教区]]和[[天主教努奧羅教區|努奥罗教区]]。

現任總主教為{{link-de|若瑟·巴圖里|Giuseppe Baturi}}<ref name="Vatican20191116">{{cite press release |title=Rinunce e nomine, 16.11.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2019/11/16/0882/01840.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-11-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191117130358/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2019/11/16/0882/01840.html |archivedate=2019-11-17 |language=it |date=2019-11-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休總主教為{{link-en|若瑟·馬尼|Giuseppe Mani}}和{{link-en|亨利·米廖|Arrigo Miglio}}<ref name="Vatican20191116" /><ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 25.02.2012 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2012/02/25/0120/00272.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-11-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191117133905/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2012/02/25/0120/00272.html |archivedate=2019-11-17 |language=it |date=2012-02-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

